description:
@SharkTankGlobals @kevinoleary exposes the #1 reason youre not rich.
He shares the $28 habit thats draining your wallet  and how to 10x your income without working harder.

 Learn the wealth rule that changed his life
 The biggest lie about investing
 Why your relationship could destroy your finances

 Full episode: https://youtu.be/mpAZehPviLQ
